Product Description

UGREEN SATA to USB C Adapter Cable for 2.5" SSD and HDD Hard Drive Adapter Support SATA III UASP 5Gbps Data Transfer Speed with 1.5FT Cable

Hard Drive Upgrade & Clone

UGREEN USB-C to SATA III Adapter cable enables quick access to 2.5" SSD and HDD, and offers an easy way for booting up old hard disks, upgrading PC storage, cloning hard disks, recovering & retrieving data of decommissioned laptops, and expanding storage. You are free of opening a computer panel for troublesome installation. More effective and convenient.

5Gbps Fast Speed w/ UASP Accelerated

Features latest SATA III 6Gbps and USB C 3.1 Gen 1 5Gbps which delivers blazing data transmission rate up to 5Gbps. Enhanced with accelerated transmission protocols-UASP (USB Attached SCSI Protocol) and TRIM, the SATA III to USB-C Adapter enables you to take the full advantage of SSD drives and realize 70% faster than traditional HDD drives.

Simple to Use

  • USB-bus powered, no need for extra power supply for 2.5" SATA HDD/SSD.
  • Plug & play, driver-free for all devices.
  • Support hot-swapping. No need to swith off your laptop while exchanging the connected hard disks.
  • LED indicator lets you learn the working status of this External Hard Disk Reader easily.

Outstanding Performance

*Smart Auto Sleep Mode: The USB to SATA Adapter Cable features 3-min Auto Sleep Mode to let your HDD or SSD stop spinning to have a rest. Good to extend the lifespan of the hard drives.

*Integrated USB-C Cable: This SATA to USB C cable is built with a 50cm cable that makes it work out the box. No need to worry that the cable gets lost.

*Advanced Chipset: The prominent ASM1153E chip not just ensures stable and fast data transfer but significantly improves security to your files.

*S.M.A.R.T Supported: Features S.M.A.R.T function and allows you to check the status of your HDD or SSD on computer easily. Note: to use this function, both the computer and SATA HDD SDD should support S.M.A.R.T function.

Universal Compatibility

*USB-C Male Connection: Laptops running Windows 10/8.1/8/7/XP/Vista, Mac OS, Linux or Chrome OS. Compatible with MacBook Pro, MacBook Air, Huawei Matebook X Pro, Google Chromebook Pixel, Dell XPS 13/15, Lenovo Yoga 900 720, HP Spectre notebook, Envy 13, etc.

*SATA 15+7 Pin Female Connection: 2.5" SATA III / II / I HDD and SSD, compatible with Seagate Barracuda HDD 2.5", Samsung 860 EVO/850 EVO SATA III SSD, WD Blue/Green 2.5 SATA SSD, SanDisk SSD PLUS, SanDisk Ultra 3D SSD, Crucial BX500/MX500/MX300, PNY CS900, TOSHIBA TR200/Q300, DREVO X1, Gigabyte, YUCUN 2.5" SSD etc.

Warm Reminder

Not support 3.5" SATA hard drives and IDE drives.

If your hard drive is new, please make a partition before using it.

If your hard drive is old and it doesn't work, please back up the data first and then make a partition for a try.

      Il prodotto funziona bene in quanto a stabilit del segnale e velocit di trasferimento ma devo segnalare, purtroppo, una fastidiosa caratteristica della sua costruzione.
      Posseggo molti attrezzi di natura simile, tutti USB 3.1 A, e con questi l'attacco del cavo all' Hard Disk o SSD avviene in maniera sicura ma comunque morbida, senza fare troppa pressione o sfregare sui contatti.

      L'unico vantaggio che questo comporta che una volta inserito la presa rimane saldissima, ma secondo me non vale la pena di possibili danni agli SSD.
      Lo continuer comunque a tenere per emergenza e per un uso saltuario, ma consiglio di acquistare altri modelli.
